title: Rock Fall to stand alongside sire at WinStar
text: Rock Fall to stand alongside sire at WinStar Friday, 2 October 2015 (6 minutes ago) ROCK FALL, winner of the Grade 1 Vosburgh Stakes at Belmont on Saturday, will stand alongside his sire Speightstown at WinStar Farm in Kentucky when he retired at the end of the year.
